<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002171> <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#is_class_level> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002171> <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#is_metadata_tag> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
