<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002175> <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#is_metadata_tag> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002175> <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#shorthand> "present_in_taxon" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002175> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The SPARQL expansion for this relation introduces new named classes into the ontology. For this reason it is likely that the expansion should only be performed during a QC pipeline; the expanded output should usually not be included in a published version of the ontology." .
