<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0006939> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "smooth muscle contraction" .
_:B6182a376bb91faf23c041c37927ea26d <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Axiom> .
